{"tid":1650681,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[十八區開花] 土瓜灣攻略","createTime":"2019-10-13T05:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T08:37:03.000Z","uid":40855,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff82a926ecd415495758ff94050b8a7d0f978f61","tid":1650681,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"1. 工聯會十字路好近九龍城差館，要保護手足，富寧街同天光道都一定要有路障阻礙對方前進。<br />\n<br />\n2. 一旦堵路，唔可以再放車，路面暢順一分，差人容易推進一分，各區手足危險多一分。<br />\n<br />\n3. 除咗中銀，創興工商都係中資。<br />\n<br />\n4. 有人目標係交通燈，就算唔認同，都請唔好阻人爆，聽日要全民被迫罷工。<br />\n<br />\n5. 集合地點上次係新公，今次見文宣係馬頭圍，而無論如何，工聯會十字路都一定係聚腳點。"},{"pid":"8f481056ded3570870b79a88b80d77f092080f9d","tid":1650681,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:46:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f6fbf94e374b6b6d5c7bac131068e8e509f1982","tid":1650681,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"放上你個區嘅tg grp!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9397762e3b260c5a2514c84debd7575f951209c2","tid":1650681,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:12:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c86e079b96d00438372938cee34a28af629f7874","tid":1650681,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:13:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f840bbb995899bdb87487d96ce67016cb2bee22a","tid":1650681,"uid":151539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fb300ad1c503a35124942d46428dd908d70e62c","tid":1650681,"uid":93880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:40:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6aeac0a8433c415ffde0e61c751782d791657680","tid":1650681,"uid":93880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e98da0908694e4b44acb4dd898d28c840b931eaa","tid":1650681